{"tid":264452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佛都有火】「女體盛」索模被非禮？ 彈起身同食客片過","createTime":"2017-05-30T23:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T02:44:45.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b08b31dce9586d58dc6000518ea3466629f336","tid":264452,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496150933_ca85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496150933_ca85.jpg&h=d5f86728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496146390_54ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496146390_54ca.jpg&h=e7607630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496146391_0df7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496146391_0df7.jpg&h=2b6b3ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496146392_c0af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496146392_c0af.jpg&h=3aef55f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵食艱難，但並不代表可以任人魚肉！山西太原就有一名模特兒，在當地一間餐廳做「女體盛」，身上放滿壽司、魚生供食客享用，誰知遭一名男顧客「鹹豬手」。模特兒不忿被非禮，一時火起不理身上放着的壽司，起身和涉事顧客理論，還用壽司掟向對方，隨後雙方更打起上來。<br />\n<br />\n據搜狐網報道，這間餐廳為了招攬食客光顧，特別找了不少女模特兒辦「女體盛」宴會。不過活動開始沒多久，一名躺着枱上全身放滿食材的女模特兒，突然坐了起來，和旁邊一名男子發生激烈爭吵。<br />\n女模特兒認為男子在取餐的時候摸了她身上某處部位，但男子說沒有。期間，女子還用食物扔向男子並動手打他。有網友指，事件發生在本月26日。事後，該店家對事件並沒有作出任何回應，不確定是衝突還是故意安排。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170531/56762205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170531%2F56762205&d=o1PnGbzvBgrRCns9BvjyqTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=25f4d76a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170531%2F56762205&h=11c15266\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170531/56762205</a>"},{"pid":"b5e32d49d430a41b9897ac031b290d7f72a77c30","tid":264452,"uid":84998,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:26:42.000Z","msg":"做雞做得咁唔專業"},{"pid":"138bead0e0e93d51dcd44c0d35db3e95931d86c0","tid":264452,"uid":35814,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"條女咁嘅樣又唔係除晒....<br />\n請都唔去啦"},{"pid":"500210d6effb70ecd5facc7f5dff11d1197154b3","tid":264452,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女咁嘅樣又唔係除晒....<br />\n請都唔去啦</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"6ed974df025c4f154c543a323fce50d2386b7f86","tid":264452,"uid":102056,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"773c301009842968eb668cdc59b287ef7357d241","tid":264452,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:34:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"276b87beacd8b73ef2d8b7fc935409534b9f0157","tid":264452,"uid":46454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:40:37.000Z","msg":"記得係舊登睇過個post,有位巴打去日本見客嗰陣試過一次女體盛,人地就真係當條女係一隻碟咁,唔可以有任何動作,估唔到呢d非常講求mutual respect的野咁夠膽死係支那照辨煮碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18027e8f89113e5d439279bb1784fe9a25a3ff8c","tid":264452,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15f1f1781999766a6da877be7e70936f0507b46","tid":264452,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"